706-8\n|ref=harv\n}}\n* {{cite book\n|last=Torbus\n|first=Tomasz\n|title=Nelles Guide Poland\n|year=1999\n|publisher=Hunter Publishing\n|location=Munich\n|isbn=978-3-88618-088-2\n|ref=refTorbus1999\n}}\n* {{cite book\n|last=Urbankowski |first=Bohdan |authorlink=Bohdan Urbankowski\n|year=1997\n|title=J\u00f3zef Pi\u0142sudski: Marzyciel i strateg |trans-title=J\u00f3zef Pi\u0142sudski: Dreamer and Strategist\n|volume=1\u20132\n|location=Warsaw\n|publisher=Wydawnictwo ALFA\n|language=pl\n|isbn=978-83-7001-914-3\n|ref=harv<!--refUrbankowski1997-->\n}}\n* {{cite book\n|last=Vital\n|first=David\n|year=1999\n|title=A People Apart: The Jews in Europe, 1789\u20131939\n|publisher=Oxford University Press\n|isbn=978-0-19-821980-4\n|ref=harv\n|url=https://archive.org/details/peopleapartjewsi00vita\n}}\n* {{cite journal\n|last=Wandycz |first=Piotr S. |authorlink=Piotr S. Wandycz\n|year=1990\n|title=Poland's Place in Europe in the Concepts of Pi\u0142sudski and Dmowski\n|journal=East European Politics & Societies\n|volume=4 |issue=3\n|pp=451\u201368\n|ref=harv\n}}\n* {{cite book\n|last=Watt |first=Richard M.\n|year=1979\n|title=Bitter Glory\n|location=New York City\n|publisher=Simon and Schuster\n|isbn=978-0-671-22625-1\n|ref=harv\n}}\n* {{cite book\n|last=Wein|first=Berel\n|year=1990\n|title=Triumph of Survival: The Story of the Jews in the Modern Era 1650\u20131990.\n|publisher=Shaar / Mesorah\n|isbn=0-89906-498-1-\n|ref=harv\n}}\n* {{cite book\n|last=W\u0142adyka |first=W\u0142adys\u0142aw\n|year=2005\n|title=Z Drug\u0105 Rzeczpospolit\u0105 na plecach. Posta\u0107 J\u00f3zefa Pi\u0142sudskiego w prasie i propagandzie PRL do 1980 roku\n|ref=harv\n}} In {{harvnb|Jab\u0142onowski|Kossewska|2005|}}.\n\n* {{cite book\n|last=Zamoyski\n|first=Adam\n|authorlink=Adam Zamoyski\n|year=1987\n|title=The Polish Way\n|location=London\n|publisher=John Murray\n|isbn=978-0-531-15069-6\n|ref=harv\n|url=https://archive.org/details/polishwaythousa00zamo\n}}\n* {{cite book\n|last=Zimmerman |first=