ographical Dictionary]] (Polski S\u0142ownik Biograficzny) vol. XXVI\n|year=1981\n|publisher=Polska Akademia Nauk\n|location=Wroc\u0142aw\n|isbn=\n|pages=311\u2013324\n|language=pl\n}}\n*{{cite journal\n|last=Hauser\n|first=Przemys\u0142aw\n|others=Dorosz, Janina (transl.)\n|title=J\u00f3zef Pi\u0142sudski's Views on the Territorial Shape of the Polish State and His Endeavours to Put them into Effect, 1918\u20131921\n|journal=Polish Western Affairs\n|year=1992\n|issue=2\n|location=Pozna\u0144\n|pages=235\u2013249\n|publisher=Komisja Naukowa Zachodniej Agencji Prasowej\n|issn=0032-3039\n}}\n*{{cite book\n|last=J\u0119drzejewicz\n|first=Wac\u0142aw\n|authorlink=Wac\u0142aw J\u0119drzejewicz\n|title=J\u00f3zef Pi\u0142sudski 1867\u20131935\n|year=1989\n|publisher=Wydawnictwo LTW\n|location=Wroc\u0142aw\n|isbn=978-83-88736-25-4\n}}\n*{{cite book\n|last=Pi\u0142sudska\n|first=Aleksandra\n|authorlink=Aleksandra Pi\u0142sudska\n|title=Pilsudski: A Biography by His Wife\n|year=1941\n|publisher=Dodd, Mead\n|location=New York\n|oclc=65700731\n}}\n*{{cite book\n|last=Pi\u0142sudski\n|first=J\u00f3zef\n|author2=Gillie, Darsie Rutherford\n |title=Joseph Pilsudski, the Memories of a Polish Revolutionary and soldier\n|year=1931\n|publisher=Faber & Faber\n}}\n*{{cite book\n|last=Pi\u0142sudski\n|first=J\u00f3zef\n|title=Year 1920 and its Climax: Battle of Warsaw during the Polish-Soviet War, 1919\u20131920, with the Addition of Soviet Marshal Tukhachevski's March beyond the Vistula\n|year=1972\n|publisher=J\u00f3zef Pi\u0142sudski Institute of America\n|location=New York\n|asin=B0006EIT3A\n}}\n*{{cite book\n|last=Reddaway\n|first=William Fiddian\n|title=Marshal Pilsudski\n|year=1939\n|publisher=Routledge\n|location=London\n|oclc=1704492\n}}\n*{{cite book\n|last=Rothschild\n|first=Joseph\n|title=Pilsudski's Coup d'\u00c9tat\n|year=1967\n|publisher=Columbia University Press\n|location=New York\n|isbn=978-0-231-02984-1\n}}\n*{{cite journal\n|last=Wandycz\n|first=Piotr S.\n|title=Polis