YMC&pg=PA79 p. 79]}}.</ref>\n\n<ref name=ColuEncyclPoland>{{cite web |url=http://encyclopedia2.tfd.com/Poland |title=Poland |accessdate=29 December 2007 |work=[[Columbia Encyclopedia]]}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Crowds urge Poland to banish Archbishop; Pilsudski Legionnaires also Assail Catholic Church on the Removal of Marshal's Body\">{{cite news|title=Crowds urge Poland to banish Archbishop; Pilsudski Legionnaires also Assail Catholic Church on the Removal of Marshal's Body|url=https://www.nytimes.com/1937/06/26/archives/crowds-urge-poland-to-banish-archbishop-pilsudski-legionnaires-also.html|work=The New York Times|date=26 June 1937|accessdate=14 December 2009 | first=Wireless | last=To}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=Lerski96_439>{{harvnb|Lerski|1996|loc=[https://books.google.com/books?id=S6aUBuWPqywC&pg=PA439 p. 439].}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=BidJef98_186>{{harvnb|Bideleux|Jeffries|1998|loc=[https://books.google.com/books?id=6Eh9KQTrOckC&pg=PA186 p. 186].}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=Davies05_40>{{harvnb|Davies|2005|loc=[https://books.google.com/books?id=9Tbed6iMNLEC&pg=PA40 p. 40].}}</ref>\n<ref name=Davies03_00>{{harvnb|Davies|2003|}}</ref>\n<ref name=Davies05_10>{{harvnb|Davies|2005|loc=[https://books.google.ca/books?id=9Tbed6iMNLEC&pg=PA10 10]}}.</ref>\n<ref name=Davies03_95ff>{{harvnb|Davies|2003|loc=p. 95ff.}}</ref>\n<ref name=Davies03_225>{{harvnb|Davies|2003|p=225}}.</ref>\n\n<ref name=Figes96_699>{{harvnb|Figes|1996|p=699}}. \"Within weeks of Brusilov's appointment, 14,000 officers had joined the army to fight the Poles, thousands of civilians had volunteered for war-work, and well over 100,000 deserters had returned to the Red Army on the Western Front\".</ref>\n\n<ref name=ICRAP>{{cite web |title=Bronis\u0142aw Piotr Pi\u0142sudski  \u2013 Calendar of events |website=ICRAP |url=http://panda.bg.univ.gda.pl/ICRAP/en/BPcv-eng.html |accessdate =2 March 2018}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=Erickson01_95>{{harvnb|Erickson|2001|loc=[https://books.google.com/books?vid=ISBN0714651788&id=rgkSxFpK